query:
SELECT ei.*, e.name as employee_name, b.name as branch_name 
FROM employee_invoices ei 
LEFT JOIN employees e ON ei.employee_id = e.id 
LEFT JOIN branches b ON ei.branch_id = b.id 
WHERE ei.type = 'negative' 
ORDER BY ei.invoice_date DESC 
LIMIT 10;
